{"tid":2315674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"健美運動員戀上吹氣公仔　拍拖18個月拉埋天窗：我們真的很幸福","createTime":"2020-12-07T10:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:25:22.000Z","uid":253213,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"891d2ac981190e9cd092b3639d74f53f29a20cc5","tid":2315674,"uid":253213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"經常聽到「真愛無分界限」，但以下這個愛情故事，又有幾多人可以接受？繼日本有禦宅族「迎娶」動漫女角初音未來，哈薩克亦有一名健身運動員與吹氣情趣公仔「拍拖」18個月後，在親友見證之下拉埋天窗！<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克一名男演員兼健身運動員Yuri Tolochko，去年12月與吹氣公仔「女友」Margo求婚，當時他們已熱戀8個月。戀情初曝光時，Tolochko接受了不少訪問，但直至今年都遲遲未舉行婚禮，令不少網民以為他只是借「女友」炒作。<br />\n<br />\n近日，Tolochko終於上載婚禮的紀錄影片及相片。在拍拖18個月後，他們終於在親友的見證下交換戒指，並擁吻完婚，表情非常幸福。他本來計畫於今年3月舉行婚禮，但因為疫情嚴重，加上他10月因為戴金色假髮、穿上粉色裙裝在跨性別聚會上被毆打，導致腦震盪、鼻子骨折而延期。他叫網民不用擔心，指雖然較少分享與Margo的合照，但兩人的感情依然甜蜜。<br />\n<br />\n我們結婚了，別擔心，我們真的很幸福。<br />\n<br />\nTolochko曾提及2人的相識經過，是他在酒吧看到任職侍應Margo被人騷擾，於是上前解圍，互生好感發展成情侶。他們去年因為媒體報導而爆紅，但也受到不少人批評。Tolochko指Margo因此失去自信，變得沒有安全感，因此就將她帶到人類的整型醫院，請醫生為她進行整容手術：<br />\n<br />\n她（外貌）真的變了很多，一開始真的很難接受，但現在已經習慣了。<br />\n在Tolochko眼中，Margo與真人無異，是一個有思想的吹氣公仔。他指與老婆完全相愛，形容她有「非常火熱的性格」，平日會說粗口，但內心卻有著溫柔的靈魂。他們就像一般情侶一樣，會一起吃飯、去旅行，IG上更有不少放閃的照片，包括床照及鴛鴦浴的照片等等，目前IG有7.4萬位追蹤者。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYjfFte.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYjfFte.png&h=93c83745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTWBpUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTWBpUV.png&h=c016a387&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183555_3f1451d058119e043193ffb879d11ced.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183555_3f1451d058119e043193ffb879d11ced.png&h=ae2ee367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183556_daac0b41da5e9622b388333e1fdf0532.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183556_daac0b41da5e9622b388333e1fdf0532.png&h=af259cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183558_877e948df23a0a3223034fb05bc8e977.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183558_877e948df23a0a3223034fb05bc8e977.png&h=034af5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183559_db60fca3c3ee0296d73814d9741745ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183559_db60fca3c3ee0296d73814d9741745ea.png&h=6b204dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183600_69b2a97c69ec30c4e7791ef668a84ddf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183600_69b2a97c69ec30c4e7791ef668a84ddf.png&h=1a9b7438&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183601_fc4b2fc7b0f146e2c9fcc333e70b28da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183601_fc4b2fc7b0f146e2c9fcc333e70b28da.png&h=3a60ade1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/07/183603_8bd04b0062f6bc493ade8d0c5c137014.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F183603_8bd04b0062f6bc493ade8d0c5c137014.png&h=23a7f4fc&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2819987/%E3%80%90%E7%9C%9F%E6%84%9B%E7%84%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E5%81%A5%E7%BE%8E%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1%E6%88%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%B9%E6%B0%A3%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E3%80%80%E6%8B%8D%E6%8B%9618%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%8B%89%E5%9F%8B%E5%A4%A9%E7%AA%97%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%88%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2819987%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2584%25A1